      "id": 173170,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2024-03-14T01:58:40.759Z",
      "author": "BiancaT (Bianca Taylor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/xuan\">@Xuan</a>,</p>\n<p>Hm, this does look strange!</p>\n<p>Are you using the web-browser version? If so, can you please test this in an incognito window? <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/pray.png?v=12\" title=\":pray:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":pray:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 173175,
      "postNumber": 3,
      "createdAt": "2024-03-14T03:32:40.855Z",
      "author": "Xuan (Xuan)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>It may be related to resizing the browser window. Normally the first-level drop down menu is on the right, but it’s to the left:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/a/ca13cfceb9373977d8cd6977f8eaa01fafa530ad.jpeg\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-03-13 at 10.29.59 PM\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/c/a/ca13cfceb9373977d8cd6977f8eaa01fafa530ad_2_690x421.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-03-13 at 10.29.59 PM\" width=\"690\" height=\"421\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-03-13 at 10.29.59 PM</span><span class=\"informations\">2126×1300 255 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>I’m using Firefox 123.0.1.</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 173176,
      "postNumber": 4,
      "createdAt": "2024-03-14T03:36:26.094Z",
